lead_paragraph: Colorado Rockies shortstop Jose Reyes has been placed on paid leave pending completion of his criminal proceedings on domestic abuse charges in Hawaii, Major League Baseball commissioner Rob Manfred said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Rockies Reyes Put on Paid Leave Pending Abuse Case
